chunks.cleaned_english_translation: Here is a list of authors who are cited: Athanasius. Cyril. Hilary. Ambrose. Didymus. Augustine. Vigilius the African. Proclus. Agnellus. Gregory. Isidore. Prosper. Fulgentius. Hormisdas. Leo. Cassiodorus. Prudentius.
